---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import logoBlanco from '../assets/logoBlanco.png';
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-16 md:pt-24 px-4 md:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center text-center">
    <div class="w-full max-w-4xl relative">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 blur-[120px] rounded-full -z-10 animate-pulse"></div>
      <Image
        src={logoBlanco}
        alt="Uallet Logo Blanco"
        class="w-64 md:w-80 h-auto mx-auto object-contain drop-shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(216,185,255,0.4)]"
        loading="eager"
      />
    </div>
    <h1 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter leading-tight max-w-4xl mb-8">
      La nueva forma de pagar y ahorrar en el
      <span class="text-gradient">campus.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      UALlet elimina las comisiones bancarias en los pequeños pagos de la
      universidad. Ese dinero que los comercios se ahorran, se convierte
      en recompensas automáticas para ti.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-6 mb-16 md:mb-20 w-full">
      <a href="#cta" class="bg-primary-gradient text-on-primary px-6 sm:px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg active:scale-95 transition-transform flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full sm:w-auto">
        Unirse a la prueba piloto
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">rocket_launch</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#how-it-works" class="border border-outline-variant/20 hover:bg-surface-container-highest/30 px-6 sm:px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-all active:scale-95 text-on-surface inline-block text-center w-full sm:w-auto">
        Descubrir cómo funciona
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
